&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Spaulding Ridge is an advisory and IT implementation firm. We help global organizations get financial clarity into the complex, daily sales, and operational decisions that impact profitable revenue generations, efficient operational performance, and reliable financial management.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Spaulding Ridge, we believe all business is personal. Core to our values is our relationships with our clients, our business partners, our team, and the global community. Our employees dedicate their time to helping our clients transform their business, from strategy through implementation and business transformation.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Will Do and Learn&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Anaplan Associate&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;to join our &lt;strong&gt;Anaplan Delivery&lt;/strong&gt; Team!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an &lt;strong&gt;Anaplan Associate&lt;/strong&gt;, you will help some of the world’s most well-known organizations solve business challenges through Enterprise Performance Management. With the opportunity to build your Anaplan expertise by obtaining recognized certifications, you will implement Anaplan as a ‘Best in Cloud’ solution for Finance, Supply Chain and Sales.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ideal candidates will be able to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interact directly with clients to extract their needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate existing solutions, spreadsheets, and business problems into sophisticated Anaplan multi-dimensional models.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Functional Knowledge of Financial Planning &amp;amp; Analysis processes, Supply chain, Sales performance management or workforce planning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze customer needs, design, configure, and test customer solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain effective working relationships with team members&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor Analysts with domain knowledge and configuration questions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with configuration reviews to provide useful feedback&lt;/li&gt;
